MakeSpecsBetter
===============

Tired of writing bad code?
Finding it tough to maintain your spec suite?
Maybe, just maybe, MakeSpecsBetter can help you get through it.

Using cutting edge debugging tricks,
and AI patterns developed by the military,
MakeSpecsBetter will transform your Rspec suite with only a few keypresses.

"rake away the pain!"

Example
=======

got a failing spec???

>> ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/matthewrudy/MakeSpecsBetter

and a quick

 >> rake spec BETTER=true
or
 >> rake spec:better

and your troubles will be no more.

